Roll\" by [[Florida Georgia Line]], who also performed live at the event. [[Hulk Hogan]] also made a special appearance.\n{{Pro Wrestling results table\n|hide = all\n|results = <ref name=\"pwtorch.com\"/>\n|times = <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.profightdb.com/cards/wwe/tribute-to-the-troops-3914-taping-20430.html|title=WWE Tribute To The Troops '14 taping at Columbus Civic Center wrestling results - Internet Wrestling Database|website=www.profightdb.com}}</ref>\n|match1 = [[The Usos]] ([[Jey Uso]] and [[Jimmy Uso]]) defeated [[Gold and Stardust]]\n|stip1 = [[Tag team match]]\n|time1 = 8:19\n|match2 = [[Naomi (wrestler)|Naomi]] won by last eliminating [[Natalya Neidhart|Natalya]]\n|stip2 = [[Battle royal (professional wrestling)#Women's battle royal|Santa's Helper Divas Battle Royal]]{{ref|a|a}}\n|time2= 4:01\n|match3 = [[Dean Ambrose]] defeated [[Bray Wyatt]]\n|stip3 = [[Boot Camp match]]\n|time3 = 11:25\n|match4 = [[John Cena]], [[Dolph Ziggler]], [[Erick Rowan]], and [[Ryback]] defeated [[Seth Rollins]], [[Big Show]], [[Kane (wrestler)|Kane]], and [[Luke Harper]] (with [[Jamie Noble]] and [[Joey Mercury]])\n|stip4 = [[Eight-man tag team match]]\n|time4 = 9:48\n}}\n{{note|a|a}}The other participants were: [[Alicia Fox]], [[Brie Bella]], [[Cameron (wrestler)|Cameron]], [[Emma (wrestler)|Emma]], [[Nikki Bella]], [[Paige (wrestler)|Paige]], [[Rosa Mendes]] and [[Summer Rae]].\n\n=== 2015 ===\nThe 2015 edition of the special was taped on December 8 at the [[Jacksonville Veterans Memorial Arena]] in [[Jacksonville, Florida]]. It aired on December 23 on the [[USA Network]]. [[Howie Mandel]] and the band [[Train (band)|Train]] also performed live at the event. [[JoJo Offerman#Ring announcer (2013\u2013present)|JoJo]] also performed the national anthem in the beginning of the show. [[Michael Cole (wrestling)|Michael Cole]] and [[John Layfield|John \"Bradshaw\" Layfield]] were the commentators.\n{{Pro Wrestling results table\n|hide = all\n|results = <ref name=\"pwtorch.com