 (professional wrestling)|The O.C.]] ([[AJ Styles]], [[Luke Gallows]], and [[Karl Anderson]]) defeated [[Ricochet (wrestler)|Ricochet]] and [[War Machine (professional wrestling)|The Viking Raiders]] ([[Raymond Rowe|Erik]] and [[Hanson (wrestler)|Ivar]])\n|stip2  = [[Six-man tag team match]]\n|time2  = \n\n|match3 = The Kabuki Warriors ([[Asuka (wrestler)|Asuka]] and [[Kairi Sane]]) defeated [[Natalya Neidhart|Natalya]] and [[Sarah Logan]]\n|stip3  = [[Tag team match]]\n|time3  = \n\n|match4 = [[Street Profits]] ([[Angelo Dawkins]] and [[Montez Ford]]) defeated [[Curt Hawkins and Zack Ryder]]\n|stip4  = [[Tag team match]]\n|time4  = \n\n|match5 = [[Seth Rollins]] defeated [[Erick Rowan]]\n|stip5  = [[Boot Camp match]]\n|time5  = \n}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|http://www.wwe.com/shows/tributetothetroops/|''WWE Tribute to the Troops'' official website}}\n\n{{WWE}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Wwe Tribute To The Troops}}\n[[Category:Television series by WWE|Tribute to the Troops]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Iraq]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Afghanistan]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Texas]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in North Carolina]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Virginia]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Washington (state)]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Georgia (U.S. state)]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Jacksonville, Florida]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Washington, D.C.]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in San Diego]]\n[[Category:WWE international]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Series of WWE events}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:''WWE Tribute to the Troops'' results}}\nThis is a list of results from every episode of ''[[WWE Tribute to the Troops]]''.\n<!-- Commented out: [[File:WWE Trubute to the Troops logo.png|right|200px]] -->\n\n== Results ==\n\n=== 2003 ===\nThe 2003 edition of the special was taped on December 20 from Camp Victory in [[Bag