ed ways with company that year, before later appearing again for [[WWE]]. Commentators for the year's event were [[Michael Cole (wrestling)|Michael Cole]], [[Byron Saxton]], and [[John Layfield|John \"Bradshaw\" Layfield]]. [[Gabriel Iglesias]] also made a special appearance.\n{{Pro Wrestling results table\n|hide = all\n|results = <ref name=\"dwn.com\">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailywrestlingnews.com/live-wwe-tribute-to-the-troops-spoilers-from-tonight-airing-on-12142016/|title=WWE Tribute to The Troops Spoilers from Tonight, Airing on 12/14/2016 - Daily Wrestling News|website=www.dailywrestlingnews.com}}</ref>\n|times = <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://411mania.com/wrestling/csonkas-tribute-to-the-troops-review-12-14-16/|title=Csonka\u2019s Tribute to The Troops Review 12.14.16|work=411MANIA|access-date=2016-12-14|language=en}}</ref>\n\n|match1 = [[Cesaro and Sheamus]] defeated [[Primo and Epico|The Shining Stars]] ([[Primo Col\u00f3n|Primo]] and [[Epico Col\u00f3n|Epico]]), [[Luke Gallows and Karl Anderson]] and The Golden Truth ([[Goldust]] and [[R-Truth]])\n|stip1 = [[Fatal four-way tag team match]] to determine number one contenders for the [[WWE Raw Tag Team Championship]] at [[Roadblock: End of the Line]]\n|time1 = 9:35\n\n|match2 = [[Apollo Crews]] (with [[Gabriel Iglesias]]) defeated [[The Miz]] (with [[Maryse Ouellet|Maryse]])\n|stip2 = [[Singles match (professional wrestling)|Singles match]]\n|time2 = 2:30\n\n|match3 = [[The Wyatt Family]] ([[Bray Wyatt]], [[Luke Harper]] and [[Randy Orton]]) defeated [[Dolph Ziggler]] and [[American Alpha]] ([[Chad Gable]] and [[Jason Jordan]])\n|stip3 = [[Six-man tag team match]]\n|time3 = 10:15\n\n|match4 = [[Bayley (wrestler)|Bayley]] defeated [[Dana Brooke]] (with [[Charlotte Flair]])\n|stip4 = [[Singles match (professional wrestling)|Singles match]]\n|time4 = 2:30\n\n|match5 = [[Gentleman Jack Gallagher|Jack Gallagher]], [[Rich Swann]] and [[TJ Perkins]] defeated [[The Brian Kendrick]], [[Drew Gulak]], and [[Tony Nese]]