 Watkins </center>|| <center> {{Start date|1973|9|28|df=y}}</center>\n|-\n| <center> 12 </center>|| <center> 4 </center>|| <center> For Better Or Worse </center>|| <center> Jon Watkins </center>|| <center> {{Start date|1973|10|5|df=y}}</center>\n|-\n| <center> 13 </center>|| <center> 5 </center>|| <center> Not So Sweet Charity </center>|| <center> [[Peter Denyer]] & Graham Hooson</center> || <center> {{Start date|1973|10|12|df=y}}</center>\n|-\n| <center> 14 </center>|| <center> 6 </center>|| <center> Pack Up Your Troubles </center>|| <center> ''Story by:'' Roy Tuvey & Maurice Sellar<br>''Teleplay by:'' Jon Watkins</center>|| <center> {{Start date|1973|10|19|df=y}}</center>\n|}\n<br>\n===Series 3 (1974)===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! No.<br>overall !! No. in<br>series !! Title !! Writer/s !! Original Airdate\n|-\n| <center> 15 </center>|| <center> 1 </center>|| <center> The New Arrivals </center>|| <center> [[Ronald Chesney]] & [[Ronald Wolfe (screenwriter)|Ronald Wolfe]]</center> || <center> {{Start date|1974|8|16|df=y}}</center>\n|-\n| <center> 16 </center>|| <center> 2 </center>|| <center> The Invitation </center>|| <center> ''Story by:'' [[Chris Boucher]]<br>''Teleplay by:'' Jon Watkins</center> || <center> {{Start date|1974|8|23|df=y}}</center>\n|-\n| <center> 17 </center>|| <center> 3 </center>|| <center> Loot </center>|| <center> [[Myles Rudge]] || <center> {{Start date|1974|8|30|df=y}}</center>\n|-\n| <center> 18 </center>|| <center> 4 </center>|| <center> The Dinner </center>|| <center> Ronald Chesney & Ronald Wolfe</center> || <center> {{Start date|1974|9|6|df=y}}</center>\n|-\n| <center> 19 </center>|| <center> 5 </center>|| <center> Love Is All </center>|| <center> Henry Charles </center>|| <center> {{Start date|1974|9|13|df=y}}</center>\n|-\n| <center> 20 </center>|| <center> 6 </center>|| <center> She Loves Me, That Bird </center>|| <center> Jon Watkins </center>|| <center> {{Start date|1974|9|20|df=y}}</center>